thread.title: BRIEF-AO World sees 20-21 pct revenue rise for Sept quarter
thread.title_full: BRIEF-AO World sees 20-21 pct revenue rise for Sept quarter | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-AO World sees 20-21 pct revenue rise for Sept quarter
text:
Sept 21 Ao World Plc
* Strong uk revenue growth and on track to deliver on long term strategic objectives
* Expectation for quarter ended september 2015 is for overall revenue to increase year on year by 20%- 21%
* Progress in germany remains in line with plan
* Long term strategic progress of business is on-track Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reporting By London Bureau)
